OL,6,FMaureen Rickards was found guilty of
OL,7,Fthe murder of her husband in
OL,8,FCanterbury.
OL,10,FA wife, on trial for the murder of her
OL,11,Fhusband and dumping his body at the
OL,12,Fbottom of the garden, has been found
OL,13,Fguilty.
OL,15,FCanterbury Crown Court heard that
OL,16,FMaureen Rickards had subjected her
OL,17,Fhusband to a campaign of abuse in the
OL,18,Fweeks leading up to his death.
