OL,6,FJeremy Rickards, 65, had been reported
OL,7,Fmissing from the North Holmes Road
OL,8,Farea of Canterbury, Kent on 5 July
OL,9,F2024 having not been seen since 7 June.
OL,11,FFollowing efforts to find him, his
OL,12,Fwife, Maureen Rickards, 50, was
OL,13,Farrested. Forensic teams attended the
OL,14,Faddress and three properties were
OL,15,Fcordoned off.
