OL,6,FJeremy Rickards, was stabbed
OL,7,Frepeatedly in June 2024, with the
OL,8,Fpostmortem showing he had also been
OL,9,Fstrangled in the weeks before his
OL,10,Fdeath and that he was also recovering
OL,11,Ffrom recent rib fractures.
OL,13,FWitnesses who saw him before his death
OL,14,Fand saw the extent of his injuries,
OL,15,Fincluding a large cut on his forehead
OL,16,Fand bruising to his eyes and ears,
OL,17,Fwere so concerned that they urged him
OL,18,Fto get hospital treatment.
