OL,6,FIn the weeks following Jeremy's
OL,7,Fdisappearance, Rickards used his bank
OL,8,Fcards to go shopping in Canterbury,
OL,9,Fbefore messaging their daughter using
OL,10,Fthe victim's phone to say that her
OL,11,Ffather had arrived in Saudi Arabia.
OL,13,FTheir daughter was concerned about the
OL,14,Fstyle of messages and asked if her
OL,15,Fmother had taken over her father's
OL,16,Fphone.
