OL,6,FLater, she put his body in a bag and
OL,7,Fdragged it down the stairs into the
OL,8,Fgarden.
OL,10,FRickards had arranged for the garden
OL,11,Fto be tidied up and used the grass
OL,12,Fcuttings and leaves to cover the bag
OL,13,Fand leave his body to decompose.
OL,15,FWhen arrested, Maureen kept up the
OL,16,Fact, asking "what body?"
