OL,6,F"Despite her efforts to disguise what
OL,7,Fshe had done; Maureen has today been
OL,8,Fbrought to the justice for her
OL,9,Fhusband's brutal murder. Our thoughts
OL,10,Fremain with Jeremy's family and
OL,11,Ffriends at this difficult time."
OL,13,FThroughout the trial, she denied
OL,14,Fmurder. On 13 March 2025, a jury at
OL,15,FCanterbury Crown Court found her
OL,16,Fguilty.
